{"tid":199918,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話香港係文化沙漠真係冇講錯","createTime":"2017-04-13T14:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T15:25:30.000Z","uid":95541,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc35fa3051eec2b90ffe482012f5e398edb2094f","tid":199918,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:12:35.000Z","msg":"由BOMBA事件可以睇到，香港人唔單止唔支持本土文化，甚至係眨低本土文化。<br />\n<br />\n其實收費有咩問題?租場、設備、演員通通都要錢，唔收錢，佢地點樣生活?有好多外國YouTuber，都係咁做架啦。你想支持咪比錢，唔支持咪唔比錢，當條片冇到囉，何必去攻擊人地條片係垃圾呢?<br />\n<br />\n有人可能會話:想收錢可以有其他方法架姐。<br />\n有咩方法?賣廣告又被人屌，唔賣廣告又唔比收錢，老奉比片你睇咩。<br />\n<br />\n根本現在香港陷入左惡性循環:<br />\n創作收錢或賣廣告，比人屌，然後無人敢創作或者唔會係全職做創作。<br />\n最後我地就話香港係文化沙漠。<br />\n根本香港搞成咁係我地一手造成。<br />\n當然，都可以話係本土創作人唔夠毅力，堅持唔到落去。<br />\n但係我地係咪應該要為佢地塑造一個良好的創作環境比佢地呢?"},{"pid":"f480e393a59b48f1e3b23db675d53664d88151a5","tid":199918,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:32:22.000Z","msg":"bomba同文化有關係？"},{"pid":"d9f9293b43250e318f777957955bc27a7074f211","tid":199918,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bomba同文化有關係？</blockquote><br />\n影片創作唔係創作的一部份?"},{"pid":"6aedc98d8dbc18d88d0467565c7e4fff92a95164","tid":199918,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"算啦 香港人係咁 乜都鍾意屌<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔屌唔安落"},{"pid":"1123c7d539868da4944719decad288d884ddeeec","tid":199918,"uid":103004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>bomba同文化有關係？</blockquote><br />\n影片創作唔係創作的一部份?</blockquote><br />\n影片當然係創作一部份<br />\n但人地話bomba冇文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed2c41a38680fa87c7b7111bcdef59c512cf282","tid":199918,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>bomba同文化有關係？</blockquote><br />\n影片創作唔係創作的一部份?</blockquote><br />\n影片當然係創作一部份<br />\n但人地話bomba冇文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇文化就見仁見智啦<br />\n不過其實都係想講返香港冇一個適合創意的環境"},{"pid":"a990309d5abda169ddb614f95d871b724accb821","tid":199918,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"咁撚垃圾學人收錢？<br />\n達哥條貪錢狗都未夠收啦"},{"pid":"5be1895beb56eb57213f5555eb86cb46e181fbd2","tid":199918,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚垃圾學人收錢？<br />\n達哥條貪錢狗都未敢收啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"43178e1b4308b132c74d01731c49814a0b0790c7","tid":199918,"uid":34876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都認同香港係文化沙漠<br />\n但bomba被人屌既最大原因 係佢d片本身垃圾 <br />\n唔好再講到bomba係受害者咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b4511953db95588c9a6835b327baa2daab245b","tid":199918,"uid":4104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:10:30.000Z","msg":"BOMBA有乜文化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚垃圾學人收錢都唔屌得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720ddc88ad151a1dfb5735ad557c494e0cb7d9b1","tid":199918,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"文化收錢是ok的<br />\n但你都要值先得架&hellip;"},{"pid":"5fdcf57629cfe5394cf8b27b5b7793659b793c65","tid":199918,"uid":10721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"記得去支持袁生"},{"pid":"f230644e0280055fe95cafc753f9ffb2a060db59","tid":199918,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"或者佢地的片係真係垃圾，但垃圾唔代表我地有權去侮辱佢地的創作係咪?"},{"pid":"62a9375721361309c6a45fcab8cbfefa08a33343","tid":199918,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:25:30.000Z"